{"tid":1658981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[大事] 挪威議員提名港人角逐諾貝爾和平獎！！！","createTime":"2019-10-16T17:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T17:29:17.000Z","uid":320849,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d46d09ef97d3a31eeb0e75b4f0d2314f7adb59cf","tid":1658981,"uid":320849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">挪威國會議員<strong>梅爾比</strong>提名香港人角逐出年嘅諾貝爾和平獎。大家繼續努力啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>挪威一名國會議員近日訪港後提名香港人角逐明年的諾貝爾和平獎。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">挪威國會議員<strong>梅爾比</strong>，指港人每天冒著生命及安全風險挺身爭取言論自由及基本民主，值得獲和平獎，希望能進一步鼓勵這場運動。</span>梅爾比是首都奧斯陸選區的自由黨議員， 2017 年上任至今，上月底訪港時分別與示威者還有多名泛民議員交流。她指不少人都強調這是一場群眾自發的運動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">消息來源：<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/559378/即時新聞/挪威議員倡港人角逐諾貝爾和平獎\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F559378%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%80%A1%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%80%90%E8%AB%BE%E8%B2%9D%E7%88%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E7%8D%8E&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=10c17a8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F559378%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%8C%AA%E5%A8%81%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%80%A1%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%80%90%E8%AB%BE%E8%B2%9D%E7%88%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E7%8D%8E&h=3685929b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/559378/即時新聞/挪威議員倡港人角逐諾貝爾和平獎</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>當政府再無民望，反抗就係希望！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e0b25c0b48f1f204e74cc44fd11105983a9f8ae9","tid":1658981,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail